<section class="home__projects">
  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p>
      <strong>Unique ownership information for swedish companies.</strong>
      <a href="https://www.vembi.se">Vembi</a> is a startup where you can find direct owner information for more than 30 000 companies as well as being able to see who controls over 70 000 swedish companies.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p>
      <strong>Pretty real-time stats for the live broadcast of the Ö till Ö swimrun world championship.</strong>
      The video wizards at <a href="http://fkdv.se">FKDV</a> needed a tool that fetched real-time data from the timing system and generated nice info overlays that could be inserted into the live broadcast from <a href="http://www.otilloswimrun.se">Ö till Ö</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p>
      <strong>Turning ideas into improvements in healthcare.</strong>
      <a href="http://www.genombrott.nu">Genombrott</a> (<a href="https://vimeo.com/123012724">video</a>) is a comprehensive tool for healthcare professionals from the Swedish Association of Local Authorities and Regions, currently being tested in psychiatric care.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
  <p>
    <strong>What should you order and what could you possible talk about?</strong>
    <a href="http://www.theicebreakermachine.com">The Ice Breaker Machine</a> from Tullamore Dew analyses your Facebook profile and solves both problems.
  </p>
</div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <a href="https://www.releasefest.se" class="relasefest-case-listing"><%= partial 'releasefest/releasefest_logo_4' %></a>

    <p><strong>Hooray for Swedish digital projects and products!</strong> On <a href="https://www.releasefest.se">Releasefest</a> we celebrate swedish web sites, web services, campaigns, ecommerce sites, open source projects, apps and more.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p><strong>How good are you at assessing risk?</strong> <a href="http://risker.dina.se">Play the game Dina Risker</a> that we built together with Edelman Deportivo for the insurance company Dina Försäkringar.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p><strong>Upping the game for a chocking amount of gamers.</strong> The Single Sign-On solution <a href="http://accounts.paradoxplaza.com">Paradox Accounts</a> is built to scale to handle the excitement around Paradox Interactive's games.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p><strong>Reports, analysis and insight for media professionals.</strong> <a href="https://premium.medievarlden.se">Medievärlden Premium</a> is a subscription service that gives you better intel on the changing media landscape.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p><strong>A web video platform for lawyers</strong> On <a href="https://www.bgplay.se">BG Play</a> some of Sweden's sharpest legal minds bring you news and training in various legal areas.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p><strong>Tapped into your beast mode on that last run?</strong> Give it the presentation it deserves. <a href="http://gpx.io">GPX.io</a> is a mapping service wher eyou can upload runs (or any activity) that you want to brag to your friends about.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box-gradient-border">
    <p>
      <strong>The lack of clean water is a global crisis.</strong> By becoming a <a href="https://manadsgivare.wateraid.se">monthly donator</a> or <a href="https://gavoshop.wateraid.se">donating money in the gift shop</a> you help WaterAid save and change lives.
    </p>
  </div>
